in 1830, the church of jesus christ of latter-day saints was organized by joseph smith at fayette, n.y
in 1862, the civil war battle of shiloh began as the confederates attacked union forces in tennessee
in 1892, author and newscaster lowell thomas was born in woodington, ohio
